  title: 'Artificial Intelligence in Daily Life',
  transcript: "Artificial intelligence is now used in many everyday applications, from virtual assistants to personalised recommendations. These technologies help people save time and access information more easily. However, concerns about privacy, job displacement, and algorithmic bias continue to grow. As AI becomes more advanced, society must find ways to use it responsibly and ethically.",
